title Reservación Exitosa
style.
  
  body {
              text-align: center;
              font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
              background-color: #f0f0f0;
              display: flex;
              justify-content: center;
              align-items: center;
              height: 100vh;
              margin: 0;
          }
          
          
          .card {
              text-align: center;
              background-color: white;
              border-radius: 10px;
              box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
              overflow: hidden;
              width: 95%;
          }
          .header {
              
              background-color: #9370DB;
              color: white;
              padding: 15px;
              text-align: center;
              font-weight: bold;
          }
          .content {
              padding: 15px;
          }
          .image-container {
              text-align: center;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
          }
          .image-container img {
              max-width: 100%;
              height: auto;
          }
          .details {
              text-align: center;
              margin-bottom: 15px;
          }
          .total {
              background-color: #E0FFFF;
              padding: 10px;
              text-align: center;
              font-weight: bold;
          }
          .prohibitions {
              text-align: center;
              font-size: 0.8em;
              color: #666;
              margin-top: 15px;
          }
          .button {
              background-color: #f0f0f0;
              border: none;
              color: #333;
              padding: 10px 20px;
              text-align: center;
              text-decoration: none;
              font-size: 16px;
              margin: 15px 0;
              cursor: pointer;
              border-radius: 5px;
              width: 45%;
              
          }
  
